<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4897013>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Elevation map showing the type localities of new species and Cyrtodactylus species included in the comparisons: 1. Cyrtodactylus karsticola sp. nov. (black star); 2. C. agarwali sp. nov. (black circle); 3. C. aaronbaueri sp. nov. (black triangle); 4. C. bengkhuaiai sp. nov. (black tilted square); 5. C. montanus; 6. C. tripuraensis; 7. C. khasiensis; 8. C. jaintiaensis; 9. C. guwahatiensis; 10. C. urbanus; 11. C. septentrionalis; 12. C. kazirangaensis; 13. C. nagalandensis; 14. C. arunachalensis; 15. C. markuscombaii and C. martinstolli; 16. C. himalayicus; 17. C. cayuensis; 18. C. tamaiensis; 19. C. ayeyarwadyensis; 20. C. mandalayensis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4897013/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

